{"tid":2440816,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"隔牆有耳：犯聚徐英偉「釋法」： 電車路非公眾地方（李八方）","createTime":"2021-03-10T08:19:58.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-10T09:12:38.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"acdbff855155f634f57fc00433eb09fa0a2dccdf","tid":2440816,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:19:58.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/E4S7ZVKLORGBPHH7E5HYFYMPWU/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FE4S7ZVKLORGBPHH7E5HYFYMPWU%2F&d=QSug7dhZHD7voFbR5lwplaarsW1wokO1n9cqNe5yO8o%3D&h=0bad8ffe\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20210310%2FE4S7ZVKLORGBPHH7E5HYFYMPWU%2F&h=fe1cd698\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20210310/E4S7ZVKLORGBPHH7E5HYFYMPWU/</a><br />\n<br />\n隔牆有耳：犯聚徐英偉「釋法」：<br />\n電車路非公眾地方（李八方）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/89yaIHBKv-AHeU4n0RcZMyC7Mag=/510x287/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/FWCHBJAGRZFWXJ5UYQCUFC23K4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2F89yaIHBKv-AHeU4n0RcZMyC7Mag%3D%2F510x287%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FFWCHBJAGRZFWXJ5UYQCUFC23K4.jpg&h=195f934f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■徐英偉出席香港電車公眾免費乘車日活動，一班白衣人企埋一齊拉橫額打卡影相。<br />\n<br />\n民政事務局局長徐英偉一向鍾意玩facebook，試過喺油麻地大火期間分享食糖水相片，當網民留言質疑時居然引戰，話自己「Multi-tasking」。呢股戰狼風吹到民政局fb小編，因為一次電車活動，同中西區區議員葉錦龍嚟一場罵戰。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/BhHXVSe4ZtGN8m2pnbc1a2ynBKs=/510x115/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/RUSOP36D5FFIRHJAXZBUOSGRFA.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FBhHXVSe4ZtGN8m2pnbc1a2ynBKs%3D%2F510x115%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FRUSOP36D5FFIRHJAXZBUOSGRFA.jpg&h=e8b8d312&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■葉錦龍喺民政局fb留言，質疑局長犯聚。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n15白衣人電車路打卡<br />\n<br />\n事緣徐英偉前日出席香港電車公眾免費乘車日活動，15個「白衣人」企埋一齊拉起橫額打卡影相，仲喺城西道馬路電車路上鋪紅地毯做揭幕儀式。又唔使俾人票控599G，又唔使上返行人路，雙重標準惹嚟中西區區議會石塘咀選區議員葉錦龍不滿。佢喺民政局fb留言質疑，點解局長又群聚又發表政治就得，但其他人喺高等法院排隊聽審，揸住張籌都俾PoPo告違限聚令？<br />\n<br />\n結果民政局喺留言答，話徐英偉應邀出席，活動只接受獲邀請嘉賓出席，活動地點唔屬於公眾地方所以無違反限聚令。葉錦龍就貼埋張圖反問「嗰個位電車路嚟喎局長」，市民都好想知點解唔係公眾地方。不過fb編輯就冇再回應。有人就心水清，官話唔係公眾地方，咪唔係囉！<br />\n<br />\n李八方<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jxkq-Eiq1xXaN4O6ebDKL5m7mEI=/510x153/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ALQAAR24F5H6ZCON5WHMO4YLX4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fjxkq-Eiq1xXaN4O6ebDKL5m7mEI%3D%2F510x153%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FALQAAR24F5H6ZCON5WHMO4YLX4.jpg&h=833472dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■民政反駁，指地點唔屬於公眾地方喎。"},{"pid":"cb6d381f2e38652c87e53ec36ba701aaf44095c7","tid":2440816,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:21:24.000Z","msg":"如何定義公眾地方？<br />\n公眾地方<strong><span class=\"red\">指當其時公眾人士或部分公眾人士可以或獲准在繳費或不繳費下進入的任何地方</span></strong>。如私人物業（例如商鋪）在某些時候容許公眾人士進入，該私人物業就會符合公眾地方的定義<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7173d5abe208226ea2d5bd18d33ad79590c3415","tid":2440816,"uid":290404,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-10T08:21:42.000Z","msg":"有官員就唔係公眾地方，有黃絲就係公眾地方，完"},{"pid":"2430c074c80278bd094fe1ae3ebd9f5cdfa94e42","tid":2440816,"uid":18477,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cb6d381f2e38652c87e53ec36ba701aaf44095c7","tid":2440816,"uid":77196,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1